article_title: GNC Says Outside Testing of Nutritional Supplements Found No Improper Labeling
article_text:
Outside testing of some GNC Holdings Inc. nutritional supplements found no improper labeling, the retailer said Tuesday.

The Pittsburgh retailer didn’t disclose details of the testing, which was conducted by Eurofins.

The testing comes as New York Attorney General Eric T. Schneiderman has been investigating several companies, including...
